// (so paths are e.g. "routing.py", "dependencies/utils.py"). If you index the
// repo root instead, prefix each with "fastapi/".
//
// 100 questions, 25 holdout. The first ~45 are hand-written and grep-verified
// (factual / how-to / where / cross-file / out-of-scope, incl. 15 hard multi-hop
